<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA68">
<l>cilampaṭiyā ḷūṭalait tāṉṟavirppāṉ vēṇṭic</l>
<l>cilampaṭimēṟ cevvarattañ cērtti - nalampeṟ</l>
<l>ṟetirāya cekkariṉu mikkōlañ ceytāṉ</l>
<l>mutirā matiyāṉ muṭi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Needing to dispel the sulking of her with ankleted feet</l>
<l>he joins [his] crown to the red ointment on [her] ankleted feet,</l>
<l>the one with the immature moon who made this beauty more red</l>
<l>than the evening sky that was opposite him, obtaining beauty.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
